layer 和其他地方观看音乐节（如果您无法观看）确保获得门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish And The Bottlemen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>是今年音乐节的六大主角。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">,</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c"> </a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">Pendulum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenny-beats">Kenny Beats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Neck-Deep">Neck Deep</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">The Wombats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hak-baker">Hak Baker</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>等也有望参演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024"><i>请返回 NME，</i></a><i>了解雷丁和利兹 2024 年的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。</i></p><p> 《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-2024-heres-what-went-down-at-fred-again-s-headline-set-3786798">阅读 2024：这又是 Fred 的遭遇》一文的头条新闻</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
